Mikohn says exterior margins increasing . Mikohn Gaming Corp said Tuesday profit margins , especially in exterior signs , are increasing . Mikohn said in a statement growth in its core interior signage business primarily reflected casino remodeling and refurbishing . Mikohn said second quarter gross margins were 37 . 6 percent , compared with 36 . 5 percent in the first quarter , and 34 . 3 percent in the year - ago second quarter . Mikohn posted profits of $ 852 , 000 , or $ 0 . 09 a share , for its second quarter , ended June 30 , compared with $ 94 , 000 , or $ 0 . 01 a share in the comparable year - ago period . Revenues were $ 25 . 8 million compared with $ 23 million in the year - ago period . 
